---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import siteConfig from '@/site-config'
---

<BaseLayout description={siteConfig.description}>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1 class="text-title">Hi, I'm Shad Mirza</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Full-Stack Engineer • ~7 years of experience • AWS/GraphQL/React
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm a passionate full-stack engineer with expertise in building high-scale systems, mobile/web platforms, and
      serverless cloud infrastructure. I specialize in AWS, GraphQL, and React/React Native, with a proven track record
      of building scalable systems at Hashnode (130M+ monthly API requests, 160K+ MAUs).
    </p>

    <p>
      <img width="640" height="360" src="/hero.jpg" alt="Shad Mirza - Full-Stack Engineer" />
    </p>

    <h2>What I Do</h2>
    <p>I focus on delivering high-quality solutions through:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Technical Excellence:</strong> Building scalable systems with AWS serverless architecture, GraphQL APIs,
        and React/React Native applications
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Problem Solving:</strong> Migrating legacy systems, improving performance, and reducing technical debt
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Collaboration:</strong> Mentoring engineers, leading cross-functional teams, and contributing to open-source
        projects
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Innovation:</strong> Implementing AI-powered features, CI/CD pipelines, and modern development practices
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>My Expertise</h2>
    <p>Here are the key areas where I excel:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Full Stack Development:</strong> TypeScript, Node.js, Express, REST APIs, GraphQL, Redux, MobX, Next.js,
        React.js, React Native
      </li>
      <li><strong>Backend & Databases:</strong> MongoDB, Redis, PostgreSQL</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Cloud & Infrastructure:</strong> AWS (Lambda, API Gateway, Step Functions, EventBridge, S3, EC2, SQS, SNS),
        Serverless Architecture, Infrastructure as Code (SST, AWS CDK)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Tools & Practices:</strong> CI/CD, TDD, Jest, Cypress, TailwindCSS, Styled Components
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Recent Experience</h2>
    <p>
      Currently working as a <strong>Senior Software Engineer</strong> at <strong>Hashnode</strong>, where I've
      contributed to AWS serverless infrastructure supporting 160K+ MAUs and built GitHub sync via webhooks + Lambda
      (auto-published 1k+ docs). I also developed an AI documentation assistant using OpenAI, LangChain, and Pinecone,
      and migrated REST to Serverless GraphQL handling 130M+ requests/month.
    </p>

    <p>
      As the <strong>Mobile App Lead</strong>, I built Hashnode's React Native app from scratch (50K MAUs), implemented
      deep-linked auth, CI/CD, analytics, and complex animations (boosted rating by 36%). I reduced crash reports by 60%
      through TDD workflows and mentored 5+ engineers.
    </p>

    <p>
      Previously, I worked at <strong>Sheevoot Int Pvt. Ltd.</strong> as a Mobile Application Engineer, where I designed
      and developed the Easebuoy app (ride/food/car wash services) with 10K+ MAUs, integrating Google Maps/Directions APIs
      and running A/B tests with 100+ drivers/200+ vendors.
    </p>

    <h2>Open Source & Writing</h2>
    <p>
      I'm passionate about sharing knowledge and contributing to the developer community. I've created a reusable <a
        href="https://github.com/iamshadmirza/react-native-design-system"
        target="_blank">React Native component library & design system</a
      >
      and authored technical blogs for:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://engineering.hashnode.com/" target="_blank">Hashnode Engineering</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/react-mobx-react-native-simplified" target="_blank"
          >DigitalOcean</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://blog.logrocket.com/react-native-draggable-flatlist/" target="_blank">LogRocket</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://soshace.com/author/iamshadmirza/" target="_blank">Soshace</a>
      </li>
      <li><a href="https://alligator.io" target="_blank">Alligator.io</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      I'm always excited to take on new challenges and collaborate on interesting projects. Whether it's building
      scalable applications, optimizing performance, mentoring teams, or contributing to open-source projects, I'm
      passionate about creating solutions that drive business value.
    </p>

    <hr class="hr-line" />

    <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
    <p>Find me on</p>
    <p class="flex gap-x-4 gap-y-2 flex-wrap">
      {
        siteConfig.socialLinks.map((link) => (
          <a aria-label={link.text} href={link.href} target="_blank" class="prose-link flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class:list={[link.icon]} />
            {link.text}
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </p>

    <p>
      If you'd like to discuss potential collaborations, opportunities, or just want to say hello, feel free to reach
      out at
      <a prose-link aria-label={siteConfig.email} href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`}>
        {siteConfig.email}
      </a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
